  "link": "http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p626554/", 
  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p626554/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i1.s.hjfile.cn/entry/201407/d4c271f4-b4d1-47a1-8bab-911ac549b546.jpg\" style=\"width: 400px; height: 600px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p626554\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tMoments from the 12-year span of Boyhood which charts the growing up of a boy called Mason. Throughout the period, his parents are played by Ethan Hawke and Patricia Arquette and his sister by Lorelei Linklater who happens to be the daughter of the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/director\" target=\"_blank\">director</a>, Richard Linklater. And Richard Linklater is the man who's previously brought cinema audiences characters and situations they could grow up with, most notably in the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/trilogy\" target=\"_blank\">trilogy</a> of films, Before Sunrise, Before Sunset and Before Midnight about a couple C&eacute;line and Jesse, Ethan Hawke again with Julie Delpy who in the first film meet as youngsters on a train. The sequels <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/revisit\" target=\"_blank\">revisit</a> them at nine-year intervals through <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/separation\" target=\"_blank\">separation</a>, <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/reunion\" target=\"_blank\">reunion</a> and children. With Boyhood though, Linklater never signals the passage of time. We're left to intuit as the action progresses. When I met Richard Linklater, we started with his plans. Given that Boyhood was filmed at regular intervals over 12 years, how much was given over to chance?跨越12年的电影《少年时代》中的场景展示了一位名叫梅森的少年的成长故事。在整个拍摄期间，他的父母都分别由伊桑&bull;霍克和帕特丽夏&bull;阿奎特扮演，他的姐姐则是导演理查德&bull;林克莱特的女儿罗蕾莱&bull;林克莱特。正是理查德&bull;林克莱特在此前的作品中向观众呈现了他们有可能在成长中面对的人物和场景，其中最负盛名的当属三部曲《爱在黎明破晓前》、《爱在日落黄昏时》和《爱在午夜降临前》。三部曲讲述的是一对夫妻席琳和杰西的故事，主演同样有伊桑&bull;霍克以及朱丽&bull;德尔比。在第一部影片里，年轻的他们于火车上初次邂逅。随后的续集以九年为间隔从分离、重逢和子女等等片段再看主人公的生活变故。在《少年时代》中林克莱特却并没有突出时间的流逝，随着故事的展开我们更需要依赖直觉的判断。当我见到理查德&bull;林克莱特，我们首先讨论的是他的计划。既然《少年时代》是在12年间定期拍摄的，那这其中有多少都是随机的运气成分呢？</p>\n<p>\n\tI always kind of, knew where it was going. I was on the grade of 12 years public school for us in the US since first grade to 12th grade and then you go off to college, if you go off to college. So I felt as a kid I'd been <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/sentence\" target=\"_blank\">sentenced</a> to that like &quot;Oh Gosh, that's a long time, I'm gonna be doing this a long time, 12 years.&quot; I felt freedom was on the other side of that. And that also kind of sentence you to live in your parents' house, too. That was, everything came after that. You would be away from home and on your own. I always said that 12 years.我对影片的走向一直都很有感觉。我以12年为周期，在美国的公立学校要从1年级上到12年级，然后如果你决定去上大学的话，便会去大学。所以我小的时候一直觉得这是一种刑罚，&ldquo;哦天哪，这么长的时间。12年这么长的时间我都不能干其它事。&rdquo;我过去觉得自由只有在这一切过去之后才会出现。我也不得不住在父母家里，就像是作为惩罚。一切都在这之后才会发生。你可以远走高飞独立生活。我总是说那12年。</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江英语&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。&nbsp;</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p626554/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p626554\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p626649/\">想减肥吗？科学家发现肥胖的根源！</a></li><li styl